headline: Sip, return, repeat: What one city’s reusable cup trial taught Yum! Brands about sustainable packaging
summary: Image provided by Yum! Brands. In Petaluma, California, 32 miles north of San Francisco, Habit Burger & Grill and KFC team members recently swapped their signature red and white cups...
